author: JerryRigEverything
description:
Its time to take apart the new Samsung Z Flip 7! Get a special offer at https://www.stamps.com/jerryrig Thanks to Stamps.com for sponsoring the show! Today we see if I am able to remove the flexible inner screen without damaging the phone. Fingers crossed! 

My mini JerryRig knife can be found here: https://www.JerryRigKnife.com
title: Samsung Z Flip 7 Teardown! -- Totally Exposed
